A 31-year-old-man, identified as Princewill Okoroafor, has committed suicide. The incident happened in his apartment at Lakeview Phase 1 Estate in Amuwo Odofin, a suburb of Lagos state. It was learnt that Princewill was found dead inside his apartment with an empty container of the sniper found on his body. Confirming the incident, the spokesperson of the Lagos state police command, Bala Elkana told newsmen in the state that the scene has been investigated by the police. “One Mrs. Okereafor reported the matter at the Festac division. “The scene was visited by detectives, led by SP Francis Oyeyemi, where an open tin of suspected poisonous substance, Sniper, was recovered. “We are still investigating,” Elkana said.